  "instructions": [
    "Season the lamb cubes with salt and pepper.",
    "Heat a large skillet over medium-high heat and sear the lamb until browned on all sides.",
    "Transfer the lamb to a slow cooker and add the kaffir lime leaves, carrots, potatoes, onions, and garlic.",
    "Pour in the lamb broth and stir to combine.",
    "Cover the slow cooker and cook on low for 8 hours or high for 4 hours.",
    "About 30 minutes before serving, stir in the chopped parsley.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with additional parsley if desired."
